 with various parameters on that site."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To get the set of partical.js parameters for a specific post, the page takes the MD5 hash of the title. If your not familiar, for our purposes a 'hash' is just a mathematical function that can turn text of any length into an 128 bit number. For clarity, that number can written in hexadecimal characters. For example, applying the md5 function to"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"pre","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"Science can purify religion from error and superstition. Religion can purify science from idolatry and false absolutes.\"\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"turns it into"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"pre","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"be99a8d46c8f351619e6d3b17fb5b13a\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We can then partition that string of characters into parts. Each of these parts corresponds to a partical.js parameters. In some cases, we'll apply arbitrary math for aesthetic purposes."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Breaking down our character string:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"pre","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"be99a8 d 46c8f3 5 1 6 1 9e6d3b17fb5b13a\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":